description:
&lt;p&gt;The System Support Lead will be part of the SW region’s Strategy&lt;br /&gt;and Transformation directorate. The directorate works closely with&lt;br /&gt;the region’s performance and improvement directorate. The&lt;br /&gt;purpose of the strategy and transformation team is to support the&lt;br /&gt;development of the local health and care systems, lead the&lt;br /&gt;regional implementation of agreed national priorities for service&lt;br /&gt;transformation, shaping the provider and commissioner landscape&lt;br /&gt;and support improvements in service configuration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the System Support Lead, the post holder will lead and work as part of a&lt;br /&gt;dynamic team in delivering an effective service supporting managers and staff across the South West Region’s strategy and transformation team to support the development of integrated care systems and, working in conjunction with local system leaders, to implement changes to services configuration, operational delivery and operating models that are necessary to deliver high quality and sustainable care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Helen Crick&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Head of Transformation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: h.crick@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 07803440879&lt;/p&gt;
